<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PROJECT GLJA | Diamond Baseline v1.0</title>

    <style>
        :root {
            --neon-green: #00ff41;
            --dark-bg: #0d1117;
            --card-bg: #161b22;
            --soft-text: #c9d1d9;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: var(--soft-text);
            font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        header {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--neon-green);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--neon-green);
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,255,65,0.35);
        }

        header p {
            margin-top: 6px;
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            border: 1px solid var(--neon-green);
            color: var(--neon-green);
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .grid {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            transition: 0.25s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--neon-green);
        }

        .alert {
            border-left: 4px solid #ff3e3e;
        }

        .trust {
            border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-green);
        }

        .icon-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .icon-row img {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(0,255,65,0.25));
        }

        .agreement {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--neon-green);
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.45; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .discrepancy-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .discrepancy-list li {
            font-size: 14px;
            padding-left: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .discrepancy-list li::before {
            content: "×";
            color: #ff3e3e;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        .footer {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 18px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #586069;
            border-top: 1px solid #30363d;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>PROJECT GLJA</h1>
    <p>DIAMOND BASELINE v1.0 (LOCKED)</p>
</header>

<div class="status-badge">● STATUS: AUDIT ACTIVE & ENFORCED</div>

<div class="grid">

    <!-- LEFT CARD – ZNOJMO CASE -->
    <div class="card alert">
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; color: #fff;">ZNOJEMSKÝ PRECEDENT</h2>
        <ul class="discrepancy-list">
            <li>Systémová latence: 2,505,600 s</li>
            <li>Rozpor: 186 CZK vs Zamítnutí</li>
            <li>Procedurální nečinnost</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT CARD – TRIPLE LLM -->
    <div class="card trust">
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; color: #fff; text-align: center;">TRUST ANALYSIS</h2>

        <div class="icon-row">
            <img src="https://www.gstatic.com/lamda/images/favicon_v1_150160d13936554c2.png" alt="Gemini">
            <img src="https://anthropic.com/images/icons/apple-touch-icon.png" alt="Claude">
            <img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/modules/site/features/copilot/copilot-logo.svg" alt="Copilot">
        </div>

        <div class="agreement">AGREEMENT: 99.9%</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card" style="margin-top: 25px; max-width: 900px;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 15px;">📂 EVIDENCE & WHITEPAPER</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e;">Digitální stopa fixována přes eIDAS. 48 aktivních auditních uzlů.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    ARCHITECT: ROMAN MUŽNÝ KAŠPAR | 24.03.2026 | NO UNAUTHORIZED DILUTION
</div>

</body>
</html>
